scaledmarkets.dabl.repos

Class DummyProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • scaledmarkets.dabl.repos.DummyProvider
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RepoProvider

    public class DummyProvider
extends java.lang.Object
implements RepoProvider
    Used for testing. Does not actually interact with a repository: instead, the actions that would have been performed are recorded, and can be retrieved with the getPulledFiles and getPushedFiles methods.
